body:
Ever had those trolls, where you&#039;re stuck in-game with them, they just intentionally feed the enemy before 5 minutes even begins? Well I&#039;ve experienced that just recently and it PISSES (clearly I&#039;m tilted) me off that I got demoted by one... and the rest of my team gave up like, that was it. We need an upgrade on matchmaking or something, because I don&#039;t want others (including myself) losing LP in ranks because of these people, even worse is getting demoted by trollers, which at this point you&#039;d rather play with salty teammates.

I had to experience mine while I was at the edge of Silver 3, match was found and our teammate started stating how _LP is so important_ then started feeding every single enemy in the first 2-3 minutes. The troller then started saying:
- &quot;If you don&#039;t have the skills, don&#039;t play ranks&quot;
- &quot;As a player with no skill, you are just wasting your time and everyone else&#039;&quot;
Then my own teammates started calling me toxic and salty (cuz clearly I feel robbed), and I just couldn&#039;t do anything

Conclusion, I need a way to leave the game without losing LP and not get LPQ OR kick out teammates that are trollers, because that is the most horrible way of putting you down after you worked your butt off in this game. Sorry for the long discussion rant, what do you guys think about this problem?
